Privacy Policy

Your privacy is our top priority. AstraTax ensures that all user data is securely encrypted and processed with the highest level of confidentiality. We do not share, sell, or misuse any financial information.

1. Data Collection

We collect minimal necessary data, including uploaded tax documents and financial details, solely for providing AI-powered tax assistance.

2. Data Security

Your data is encrypted using bank-grade security and stored on secure cloud infrastructure, ensuring protection against unauthorized access.

3. Third-Party Services

We integrate Google services (Gemini AI, Cloud Vision, BigQuery ML) for AI-powered tax insights while adhering to their privacy policies.

For any privacy-related concerns, contact us at{" "} support@astratax.ai.
